title: BRIEF-ExeoTech Invest carries out SEK 2 mln directed set-off issue
text:
BRIEF-ExeoTech Invest carries out SEK 2 mln directed set-off issue Sept 16 
Sept 16 ExeoTech Invest publ AB : 
* Carries out directed set-off issue of 2 million Swedish crowns ($240,804.29) 
* 25 million shares are issued at 0.08 crown per share 
* Issue is directed towards lenders
